Color pattern (
Fig. 2
): Carapace dark brown with some golden setae. Carapace border with long, light brown setae. Coxae, labium, sternum, maxillae and ventral femora brown. Legs and palps with short, dark brown body setae and long light brown setae. Leg rings on distal femora, tibiae and metatarsi absent. Abdomen dorsum with long, light brown setae uniformly distributed, and short, black body setae forming irregular longitudinal spot on central area. Abdomen venter light brown.
